(1015, 250, 'description', 'Virizion is a stag or antelope-like, quadruped Pok√©mon that is primarily green. On the sides of its head are long horns that end in dull, curled points. It has a pointed snout with a black blaze running from its nose to the back of its head. Its face, hind legs, and underside are white. There is a pinked-tipped leaf on each side of its neck, and leafy tufts on its shoulders. On its back, there are pointed tufts of fur forming a medium-long tail. Its lower legs resemble knee-high boots with pink highlights at the knees, and it has black hooves.\r\n\r\nLike the other members of its quartet, Virizion battled against humans in order to protect Pok√©mon. Its horns are as sharp as blades, and are used to cut opponents.'),
